  "commentary": "With SPX spot at 6776.91 sitting just below the GEX flip at 6784 and massive positive gamma walls above, dealers are likely moderate sellers into any push toward 6780-6785, creating natural resistance. The PIN regime with 80B+ in total GEX suggests strong mean-reverting forces, with dealers providing liquidity by fading moves away from the 6776-6784 zone. Key levels to watch: 6780 (max positive gamma resistance), 6784 (flip strike), and 6770 (negative gamma support where dealers would amplify any breakdown).\n\nBottom line: expect price to get pinned between 6770-6785 with limited breakout potential.",
